org.openbel.framework.core.equivalence
Class StatementEquivalencer

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.core.equivalence.Equivalencer
      org.openbel.framework.core.equivalence.StatementEquivalencer

public class StatementEquivalencer
extends Equivalencer

StatementEquivalencer equivalences ProtoNetwork statements by comparing statement signatures based on global term ids. This algorithm has O(n log(n)) complexity.

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>
